          <div>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Plan anual</p>
            <h3 class="text-white text-3xl font-bold leading-snug">
              Olvídate de pagar<br>cada visita.
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
